{"tid":366074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"The Art of the Deal寫手：Trump可能於本年秋季辭職","createTime":"2017-08-19T17:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T08:39:41.000Z","uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e25dfdae51e0ccbb25c49cbfbdffde079e287e17","tid":366074,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2167135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2167135&d=8YRq65XbGL%2FGEXDebh5LywHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=9e670b6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2167135&h=251f486c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2167135</a><br />\n<br />\n〔編譯陳正健／綜合報導〕美國總統川普的影子寫手史瓦茲（Tony Schwartz）17日推文預測，川普可能因「通俄門」醜聞的司法調查，於年底前自行辭去總統大位。<br />\n<br />\n史瓦茲是川普1987年回憶錄「交易的藝術」（the Art of the Deal）的共同執筆人，曾經多次評論川普的政治生涯。<br />\n<br />\n他17日推文指出，川普即將辭去職務，在特別檢察官穆勒（Robert Mueller）及國會令他無路可退之前。<br />\n<br />\n另外，史瓦茲也表示，川普的總統任期即將告終。如果川普年底仍然在職，他將會相當驚訝。川普可能在秋季辭職。<br />\n<br />\n史瓦茲還痛批，川普有限的注意力，只會聚焦用於打擊對他的批評，以致沒有時間放在他不感興趣的政事上。"},{"pid":"11b9c9260a5ff271c8f9c314bcb602e1597fcaa0","tid":366074,"uid":4493,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T00:17:00.000Z","msg":"屌你啦 原來又係FakeNews<br />\n<br />\n呢個所謂寫手係80年代幫Trump出回憶錄嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講到佢好似係而家啲白宮寫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年Trump係支持民主黨架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9653c96331dc0e8ed6cd75bf8e46d69d54423ae","tid":366074,"